verse.name: v1
verse.lines:
He's under my feet.
He's under my feet.
Now my victory is complete.
Jesus spoiled principalities,
Made a show of them openly.
He's under my feet, he's under my feet.

verse.name: v2
verse.lines:
Love never gives up, never gives up, never gives up.
Love never gives up, never gives up, never gives up.
Love never gives up, never gives up, never gives up.
Love never gives up, till I am holy and set free.
